Description:
Won the Academy Award for most "Outstanding Picture" at the 1927/28 1st Annual Academy Awards Ceremony held May 16, 1929 before the "Best Picture" category was created for the awards given 1962 to present day.

(For the first six ceremonies, the eligibility period spanned two calendar years. For example, the 2nd Academy Awards presented on April 3, 1930, recognized films that were released between August 1, 1928, and July 31, 1929. Starting with the 7th Academy Awards, held in 1935, the period of eligibility became the full previous calendar year from January 1 to December 31.)-Wikipedia
